  "title": "Chinese Preschool Teacher 兼职幼儿教师（中文 L2）Part-Time",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Plan and implement curriculum and programmes based on Centre's curriculum framework</li><li>Design quality learning environment with developmentally appropriate learning materials and resources</li><li>Record and evaluate documentations of children's learning and development to improve planning and teaching</li><li>Collaborate with families to ensure continuity of care and learning between the home and the Centre</li><li>Commit to quality and safety of children's well-being</li><li>Participate in projects/initiatives as needed</li><li>5 hours shift</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Enjoy working with children</li><li>Committed, driven and passionate</li><li>Team player and individual contributor</li><li>Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education-Teaching (Chinese)</li><li>ECDA L2 qualified</li><li>Those currently pursuing part-time studies in early childhood education are welcome to apply.</li></ul><p>职位描述</p><ul><li>根据中心的课程框架规划和实施课程和计划</li><li>使用适合发展的学习材料和资源设计优质的学习环境</li><li>记录和评估儿童学习和发展的文件，以改进规划和教学</li><li>与家庭合作以确保家庭和中心之间的护理和学习连续性</li><li>致力于儿童福祉的质量和安全</li><li>参与社区活动并编排各节日的表演节目</li><li>工作日 5 小时轮班</li><li>学校提供教案</li></ul><p>要求</p><ul><li>热爱工作，有爱心，喜欢和孩子一起工作</li><li>注重儿童的安全，卫生和健康</li><li>有责任心，工作主动，有合作精神</li><li>工作认真，会与同事沟通和交接好相应的工作</li><li>幼儿保育和教育教学文凭</li><li>ECDA L2 合格</li><li>欢迎目前正在从事幼儿教育兼职学习的人士申请</li></ul>",
